    description:
      "Poverty in Africa has been a longstanding challenge, casting a shadow over the aspirations and dreams of millions. Within this",
    src: "/assets/images/appeals/water/Water2.jpg",
  },
  {
    title: "Serving Humanity in the UK",
    description:
      "In the UK, many people face daily challenges due to rising costs and unemployment. This includes those living below the",
    src: "/assets/images/appeals/water/Water3.jpg",
  },
  {
    title: "Winter Survival Kit",
    description:
      "As climate change intensifies worldwide, a relentless sequence of natural disasters in various countries has aggravated the difficulties faced by",
    src: "/assets/images/appeals/water/Water4.jpg",
  },
  {
    title: "Build a Masjid",
    description:
      "A mosque is the heart of the community, a place full of peace that brings the community together. In rural",
    src: "/assets/images/appeals/water/Water5.jpg",
  },
  {
    title: "Pay Zakat Online",
    description:
      "The economic situation in Pakistan has caused devastation, leaving many people in desperation. Approximately 36% of the population now lives",
    src: "/assets/images/appeals/water/Water6.jpg",
  },
  {
    title: "Women Empowerment",
    description:
      "Empowering women involves providing them with opportunities to acquire essential skills, boost their confidence, and cultivate independence, enabling lasting benefits",
    src: "/assets/images/appeals/water/Water7.jpg",
  },
  {
